The paper uses natural language processing and plagiarism detection techniques to analyze and visualize the origin of information in news articles. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and digital libraries (cs.DL).
